  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThis PR https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/pull/5029 reformatted large portions of the book due to the author's editor settings. It would be beneficial if we could define a standard format for the markdown, and check this on CI. I suspect there are several markdown linters/formatters we could choose from.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\n- Pick a markdown formatter and add a CI job that applies it to the book\r\n- Ensure that the chosen formatter is consistent with the editorconfig settings (maybe we can also lint based on editorconfig)\r\n",
